        "correctIndex": 0,
        "explanation": "$(x+2)(x+y+1)=x^2+xy+x+2x+2y+2=x^2+xy+3x+2y+2$\n$x$ と $2x$ をまとめます。",
        "difficulty": "basic"
      },
